* Pull Changes
** Why Pull?
***_ Get latest from teammates
***_ Minimize integration issues
***_ Stay up-to-date with codebase
** How to Pull
***_ Open Git dialog
***_ Select Pull
***_ Resolve conflicts if any
** After Pulling
***_ Notebook state resets
***_ Cell outputs cleared
***_ Reflects updated content
** Best Practice
***_ Pull before starting new work
***_ Pull frequently to catch conflicts early
@endmindmap
